url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/480366/exclusive-disneys-bridgit-mendlers-debut-set-for-oct-22 |title=Latest Music News, Band, Artist, Musician & Music Video News |publisher=Billboard.com |date= |accessdate=August 20, 2012}}</ref> 該張專輯在告示牌專輯榜中最高達到第30名成績。<ref>{{cite web|url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=bridgit mendler|chart=Billboard 200}}|title=Billboard Chart History: Bridgit Mendler|work=Billboard|date= |accessdate=May 13, 2010}}</ref> 並銷售至少20萬張。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://vakseen.com/site/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Soundscan-Week-26-2013.pdf|title=Week 26-2013 SoundScan Chartpack|publisher=Vakseen|accessdate=October 17, 2012}}</ref> 在國際方面，「Hello My Name Is ..」只在少數國家諸如波蘭、奧地利、英國、法國及西班牙等國家發行。<ref>{{cite web | title= Bridgit Mendlerr: Hello My Name Is... - Album Charts Week November 26, 2012| publisher=ZPAV| url=http://olis.onyx.pl/listy/index.asp?lang=en| accessdate=April 12, 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/news/41701/chartifacts---tuesday-13th-august-2013?pos=7|title=Chartifacts - Tuesday 13th August 2013|publisher=ARIA Charts|date=October 11, 2012|accessdate=September 13, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060515/http://www.ariacharts.com.au/news/41701/chartifacts---tuesday-13th-august-2013?pos=7|archive-date=2013-09-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://zobbel.de/cluk/130330cluk.txt|title=UK Charts - Hello My Name Is...|publisher=UK Charts|date=May 30, 2011|accessdate=June 4, 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.spanishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Bridgit+Mendler&titel=Hello+My+Name+Is...+Bridgit+Mendler&cat=a|title=Bridgit Mendler discography - Spain Charts - Hello My Name Is...|work=Spanish Charts |publisher=Hung Medien |accessdate=December 5, 2009}}</ref> 布莉琪的嗓音被拿來與[[莉莉·艾倫|莉莉·艾倫]]、[[雪兒·洛薇|雪兒·洛薇]]、[[潔西J|潔西J]]以及[[Karmin|Karmin]]等女歌手相比。<ref name=muchmusic/>

