===2013–至今: 即將發行第二張專輯===
2013年8月9日，布莉琪於專訪中確認，她正在進行第二張專輯的籌備，但是她得重新寫歌，因為她的筆電壞掉導致喪失掉她原本寫好的歌。<ref name=billboard2013>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5645350/bridgit-mendler-checks-in-on-touring-hurricane-single-next-album|title=Bridgit Mendler Checks In On Touring, 'Hurricane' Single & Next Album|publisher=Billboard|date=October 28, 2012 |accessdate=January 1, 2013}}</ref> 9月9日，布莉琪於推特上公布了新歌的片段。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tweetwood.com/bridgitmendler/tweet/375831296695869440|title=They gave me a minute Asked me "What will you do with it?" I took it and stretched it Into an afternoon for you|publisher=Tweetwood|date=October 28, 2012|accessdate=January 1, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202223951/http://tweetwood.com/bridgitmendler/tweet/375831296695869440|archive-date=2013-12-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 9月25日，布莉琪確認她開始於錄音室中灌錄。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ryanseacrest.com/2013/08/15/bridgit-mendler-talks-working-on-next-albu/|title=Bridgit Mendler Talks Working on Her Next Album|publisher=ryanseacrest.com|date=October 28, 2012 |accessdate=January 1, 2013}}</ref> 11月，布莉琪公布部分作品以及歌詞，包括 [[Mitch_Allan|Mitch Allan]], [[Dan_Book|Dan Book]], Alexei Misoul, Augie Ray, Beloryze 以及 Trion等歌曲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://febreteen.com.br/2013/11/bridgit-mendler-tera-ajuda-de-tres-compositores-para-novo-album/|title=Bridgit Mendler has help of three composers for new album!|publisher=Febre Teen|date=October 28, 2012 |accessdate=January 1, 2013}}</ref> 2014年2月7日，被公布布莉琪首張專其中並未與任何美國製作人合作，而且是在英國與英國的製作人 [[TMS_(production_team)|TMS]], [[Ina_Wroldsen|Ina Wroldsen]], [[Steve_Mac|Steve Mac]]以及Sean Douglas等製作人合作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hamadamania.com/2014/02/07/bridgit-mendler-collaborates-with-tms-for-sophomore-album/|title=Bridgit Mendler collaborates with TMS for sophomore album|publisher=Hamada Mania|date=October 28, 2012 |accessdate=January 1, 2013}}</ref> 2014年2月13日，布莉琪在專訪中表示將在2014年舉行夏季巡迴演唱會，屆時她的新專輯曲目也將會在演唱會當中演唱。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ktla.com/2014/02/13/bridgit-mendler-says-goodbye-to-good-luck-charlie/|title=<nowiki>Bridgit Mendler Says Goodbye to ‘Good Luck Charlie’</nowiki> |publisher=KTLA|date=October 28, 2012 |accessdate=January 1, 2013}}</ref> 3月18日，專訪中表示，其中一首新歌叫做「Rome」。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.papermag.com/2014/03/bridgit_mendler.php|title= Bridgit Mendler: Disney's Next Breakout Star|publisher=Paper Magazine|date=October 28, 2012 |accessdate=January 1, 2013}}</ref>

2014年6月28日，布莉琪從加拿大開始起跑夏季演場會。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.pe.ca/Living/Entertainment/2014-04-22/article-3697279/The-Killers-to-play-Charlottetown-July-12/1|title=The Killers and Bridgit Mendler to play Charlottetown July 12|work=The Guardian|date=May 2013|publisher=cambio|accessdate=1 June 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304052247/http://www.theguardian.pe.ca/Living/Entertainment/2014-04-22/article-3697279/The-Killers-to-play-Charlottetown-July-12/1|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 在當中她演唱新歌「Fly to You」，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bopandtigerbeat.com/2014/06/watch-bridgit-mendler-performs-new-song-fly-to-you/|title=WATCH: Bridgit Mendler Performs New Song, “Fly to You”|work=Bop and [[虎韻|Tiger Beat]]|date=May 2013|publisher=cambio|accessdate=1 June 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923193817/http://www.bopandtigerbeat.com/2014/06/watch-bridgit-mendler-performs-new-song-fly-to-you/|archive-date=2015-09-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 歌曲描述有關自我毀滅的感情，但到最後仍是值得的。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.q102.com/onair/nik-the-web-chick-26705/bridgit-mendler-debuts-new-song-12515405/|title=Bridgit Mendler Debuts New Song!!|work=Q102 FM|date=May 2013|publisher=cambio|accessdate=1 June 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924083434/http://www.q102.com/onair/nik-the-web-chick-26705/bridgit-mendler-debuts-new-song-12515405/|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>  2014年7月5日，她演唱另一首新歌「Deeper Shade Of Us」，一首迪斯可舞曲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.popline.me/?p=41447|title=Bridgit Mendler - Deeper Shade Of Us|work=Popline|date=May 2013|publisher=cambio|accessdate=1 June 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714125649/http://www.popline.me/?p=41447|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

