er and Noah Guthrie Added to Selena Gomez' UNICEF Concert|publisher=Fanlala|accessdate=July 8, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130111010740/http://www.fanlala.com/news/bridgit-mendler-and-noah-guthrie-added-selena-gomez-unicef-concert|archive-date=2013-01-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 2012年7月，布莉琪成為「Give With Target」大使，替學校募款。<ref name=target2012>{{cite web|url=http://www.disneydreaming.com/2012/07/27/bridgit-mendler-give-with-target-campaign/|title=Bridgit Mendler Give With Target Campaign|publisher=Disney Dreaming|accessdate=July 8, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108200253/http://www.disneydreaming.com/2012/07/27/bridgit-mendler-give-with-target-campaign/|archive-date=2014-11-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 該活動希望在2015年募得十億元美金。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sweetyhigh.com/blog/karma/bridgit-mendler-joins-target-to-raise-1-billion-for-schools|title=Bridgit Mendler Joins Target to Raise $1 Billion for Schools!|publisher=Sweety High|accessdate=July 8, 2012}}</ref> 為了啟動該活動，他們投資了五百萬元並分發給100個有需要的學校分別2萬5千元。<ref name=target2012a>{{cite web|url=http://pressroom.target.com/news/target-launches-5-million-campaign-236888|title=Target Launches $5 Million Campaign for Education|publisher=Target|accessdate=July 8, 2012}}</ref> 布莉琪表示：「我非常興奮能成為活動的一份子，並恭喜全國的小朋友開始的一學年。這對所有的小朋友來說能夠獲得一年所需相當重要」<ref name=target2012a/> 8月間，她透過迪士尼頻道募款500萬元，並從臉書的粉絲們募款2百萬元。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://startingpoint.blogs.cnn.com/2012/08/23/disney-darling-bridgit-mendler-helps-kick-off-nationwide-give-with-target-campaign-for-schools-in-need/|title=Disney darling Bridgit Mendler helps kick off nationwide 'Give with Target' campaign for schools in need|publisher=CNN|accessdate=July 8, 2012}}</ref>2013年3月，布莉琪參加一場反霸凌活動。<ref name=seventeen2012>{{cite web|url=http://www.seventeen.com/entertainment/features/delete-digital-drama-quotes-bridgit-mendler#slide-9|title=Spread Love, Not Hate|publisher=Seventeen Magazine|accessdate=July 8, 2012}}</ref> 關於活動，布莉琪表示：「我求學過程中也曾經歷過霸凌，而且並不有趣...我喜歡終結霸凌。人們不應該這樣對待